app.title: Supplementary Materials
app.p: The following are available online at https://www.mdpi.com/2076-3921/8/5/140/s1, Figure S1: Three-dimensional chemical structures and σ–surfaces of both volatile and non-volatile solutes, triglyceride possibilities in refined soybean oils and oil amphiphilic derivatives generated by COSMO-RS, Figure S2: Major volatile aroma compounds (VACs) in rosemary oleo-extracts determined by HS-SPME/GC-MS using (a) refined vegetable oils and (b) refined soybean oil with addition of oil derivatives as solvents, (c) the content of total monoterpenes versus total oxygenated monoterpenes in various oily solvent systems.
